        <abstract> 
<p>Describes variability in the stamens and pollen of <hi rend="italic">Lagerstroemia</hi>, which CD spoke of in <hi rend="italic">Forms of flowers</hi>.</p>  
<p>Also reports on similar phenomena in Pontederiacea (<hi rend="italic">Heteranthera reniformis</hi>).</p>  
<p>Has received from Paul Mayer an interesting paper on metamorphosis in <hi rend="italic">Palaemonetes varians</hi>, which is also being studied by J. E. V. Boas in Denmark. Shows differences between larval development in Danish forms and those found in southern Italy.</p> 
        </abstract>
